						               													<description>In the land of bread and magic, the queen has a dream: to create an ideal kingdom. Roll dice, gather resources, and use the power of your character and your tableau to build a kingdom worthy of praise!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This game uses the same system as Magical Bakery: A Conglomerate from Today, but includes additional content in its box to allow for more variety in setups and different potential for tableau building. (Note that each game is separate, and the two games cannot be combined.) Over the course of the game, you will gather resources and use them to play cards to your tableau, earning yourself victory points and additional abilities. The game ends after one player has at least 20 VP in their tableau; the player with the most points wins the game!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;On your turn, you will roll three dice (or four, for one character), with seven different types of actions available. Dice can be used to acquire cards from a common market to your hand or to generate resources in three different types (gold, influence, and magic). Resources and dice together can be used to play cards from your hand into your tableau, or to build a legendary card. Resources can be used on their own to refresh the market or be converted into the other resource types. And cards in your tableau can be used to generate special effects. Use a combination of luck and strategy to build an engine that will push you ahead of the other players in the game in order to bring the most renown to yourself and the kingdom.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Cards are Chimera size (58x90mm).&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
